    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking for a new home for my awesome car. It\u2019s been a total joy to drive and is still in really solid shape! I\u2019ve taken great care of it, so it\u2019s ready to hit the road with you right away. If you\u2019re looking for a reliable ride that still looks fantastic and handles beautifully, this is the one! Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to tell you more about it! \u2728",
