    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sound E46 M3 powered by the high-revving S54B32 inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline. This example highlights a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a limited-slip differential that provides exceptional lateral grip. The double-VANOS system has been serviced, ensuring precise variable valve timing, while the subframe has undergone a thorough inspection for stress fractures. The suspension retains its factory-spec damping characteristics with upgraded polyurethane bushings for enhanced turn-in response. While the exterior shows minor road wear consistent with high-performance use, the drivetrain remains robust with linear power delivery and a healthy compression profile across all cylinders.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 26
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
