    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s been truly loved? I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty car, and it\u2019s in great shape for its next adventure! It runs smoothly, looks sharp, and has plenty of life left in it. I've taken really good care of it, so you can just hop in and go. Feel free to reach out if you want to take it for a spin\u2014I\u2019d love for it to go to a good home!",
