      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, renowned for its individual throttle bodies and 8,000 RPM redline. This example has undergone critical preventative maintenance, including a documented double VANOS overhaul and rear subframe reinforcement to ensure structural rigidity under lateral load. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission offers precise shift gates, paired with a factory limited-slip differential that remains tight. The suspension geometry is preserved with refreshed bushings and Bilstein dampers, providing the tactile steering feedback and neutral handling balance characteristic of this chassis. Recent valve clearance adjustments and a rod bearing Blackstone report confirm the internal health of this driver-focused machine.",
